rows.label: qst701003_msg0001
rows.name:
...I'm indebted to Morumo,
that's true. But I cannot
cooperate, nor do I want to.

rows.label: qst701003_msg0002
rows.name:
I don't trust those who flee the
capital, nor those who help them.
Adel-sama, that includes you.

rows.label: qst701003_msg0003
rows.name:
You say pleasant things, but you have no real
intention of protecting Iira, do you? That's
why you help those who flee. Am I wrong?

rows.label: qst701003_msg0004
rows.name:
Those who say they want to save
everyone end up saving no one.
Your ideals can't save anyone.

rows.label: qst701003_msg0005
rows.name:
...We're done talking. I've
fulfilled my obligation. Go home.

rows.label: qst701003_msg0101
rows.name:

everyone end up saving no one.

rows.label: qst701003_msg0201
rows.name:
...These are indeed the
materials I requested. Keep
up the good work with the rest.

rows.label: qst701003_msg0202
rows.name:
In the meantime, I'll proceed
with the shelter's design.
